    "description": "如临真实战场，畅享爽快的一骑当千动作！无名英雄闯荡三国乱世的“真・三国无双”系列新作。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >■系列史上最极致的爽快感</h2>在充满紧张气氛的战场上，玩家将与铺天盖地的敌军展开殊死搏斗。该如何抵挡汹涌而来的敌人？除了凭借自己的实力，还可以与盟军协同作战，挑战“真・三国无双”系列独有的战术战役，畅享该系列史上最极致的爽快感。<br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2384580/extras/d6f0feedae291f1754bf5a5d26d74393.poster.avif?t=1771894605\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2384580/extras/d6f0feedae291f1754bf5a5d26d74393.webm?t=1771894605\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2384580/extras/d6f0feedae291f1754bf5a5d26d74393.mp4?t=1771894605\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >■以原创主角的视角展现全新的三国故事</h2>三国故事发生在广袤的中华大地上，英雄们的信念在这里交汇。本作将从原创主人公“无名英雄”的视角出发，全新描绘这个壮丽世界的魅力。<br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2384580/extras/fdf13bf7983ccc088cc30aa5975388d4.poster.avif?t=1771894605\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2384580/extras/fdf13bf7983ccc088cc30aa5975388d4.webm?t=1771894605\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2384580/extras/fdf13bf7983ccc088cc30aa5975388d4.mp4?t=1771894605\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >■PC版对应功能</h2>- 支持各种游戏控制器/手柄<br>- 可自由配置鼠标、键盘<br>- 支持4K Ultra-HD分辨率*<br>- 支持超宽显示器*<br>- 支持各种画质提升功能*<br>- 支持HDR &amp; 高刷新率*<br>*由硬件环境所决定。<br><br>※游戏画面取自开发中版本，和实际游戏内容可能有差异。<br>※ 另有《真・三国无双 起源 数字豪华版》贩售。请在购买时根据所需内容选择购买版本。",
